# Auth & Roles Rules

The platform contains multiple roles:
- Admin
- Seller
- Customer

Always separate:
- routes
- layouts
- permissions
- navigation
- dashboards

Avoid:
- mixed responsibilities
- leaking admin capabilities
- duplicated permission logic

Use:
- policies
- middleware
- role-aware navigation
- role-aware actions

Each role should have:
- dedicated UX
- dedicated flows
- dedicated dashboard/layouts where appropriate
- deffirent login and signup page
